{
  "stem": "24125.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when I told him that I'll be his friend, and who knows, after the war, maybe we'll get married, he took me there but expected favors in return.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When I joined the partisans, they were so nice that they actually made him aware that he cannot be my boyfriend because I don't wish so.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The only thing I forgot to tell you is that my friend, [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Kola, ?] he was already in the partisans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He went for a very important mission with other partisans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was caught by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And not caught red-handed, but he went to sleep over in somebody's house-- actually, not house-- where they store their winter food.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And as were they sleeping there, they were burned alive because one of the Ukrainians told them where they were.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Otherwise they would not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he died, and with him, my hope for the partisans because he was going to take me with him to the partisans.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So after that, I had no hope.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in my mind, I felt the only way for me is to go to partisans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's when I joined the partisans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What was the name of the group?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Shirlov. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mainly Ukrainians and Russians.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Russian Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were no Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if they knew, if the Jews were there, then you couldn't-- you couldn't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I, as being Jewish, recognized two members.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew, in my heart, that they were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe they knew, also.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we never exchanged information.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't ask you for any papers or proof of--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't possibly do it because I had-- first of all, I had them, and they were not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was Sophia Shman on the Ukrainian papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
